quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  92,1,Ngifunga ngobusuku uma bumboza (ngobumnyama)
  92,2,Futhi ngifunga ngemini uma ivela
  92,3,Futhi ngifunga ngalowo owadala isilisa nesifazane
  92,4,Ngempela ukuzabalaza kwenu kwehlukahlukene
  92,5,Mayelana nalowo onikezayo futhi asabe (uMvelinqangi)
  92,6,Futhi akholelwe kokuhle kakhulu
  92,7,Manjalo siyomenzela lula indlela elula
  92,8,Futhi mayelana nalowo oncishanayo futhi ozibona ukuthi
  92,9,Futhi uphika okuhle kakhulu
  92,10,Manjalo siyomenzela lula indlela eya ebunzimeni
  92,11,Futhi ayimsizi ingcebo yakhe uma esewa (efa)
  92,12,Ngempela kuphezulu kwethu ukuholwa
  92,13,Futhi ngempela ngeyethu impilo ezayo neyamanje
  92,14,Ngakho-ke nganexwayisa ngomlilo ovuthayo
  92,15,Akekho oyongena kuwona ngaphandle koyisoni kakhulu
  92,16,Lowo owaphika futhi wafulathela (endleleni eqondile)
  92,17,Futhi uyokuqhelelaniswa nabalungileyo
  92,18,Lowo onikela ngengcebo yakhe ukuze azihlanze
  92,19,Futhi akukho ngisho nakoyedwa kuyena emseni ukuze anikezwe wona
  92,20,"Ngaphandle kokufuna ubuso beNkosi yakhe, ephakeme kakhulu"
  92,21,Futhi uzothokoza